$PROB 280 phase1 2 CMT like 1004 but diff. initial on V3 $INPUT C ID TIME SEQ=DROP EVID AMT DV SUBJ HOUR TAFD TAD LDOS MDV HEIGHT WT SEX AGE DOSE FED $DATA ../data/280.csv IGNORE=C $SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 TRANS4 $PK CL=THETA(1)*EXP(ETA(1)) * THETA(6)**SEX * (WT/70)**THETA(7) V2 =THETA(2)*EXP(ETA(2)) KA=THETA(3)*EXP(ETA(3)) Q =THETA(4) V3=THETA(5) S2=V2
$ERROR Y=F*(1+ERR(1)) + ERR(2) IPRE=F
$THETA (0,10,50) (0,10,100) (0,0.2, 5) (0,10,50) (0,100,1000) (0,1,2) (0,0.75,3)
$OMEGA BLOCK(3) .1 .01 .1 .01 .01 .1
$SIGMA 0.1 0.1
$ESTIMATION MAXEVAL=9999 PRINT=5 NOABORT METHOD=1 INTER MSFO=./280.msf ;$COV PRINT=E ;$TABLE NOPRINT FILE=./280.tab ONEHEADER ID AMT TIME EVID PRED IPRE CWRES ;$TABLE NOPRINT FILE=./280par.tab ONEHEADER ID TIME CL Q V2 V3 KA ETA1 ETA2 ETA3
